  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink88-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉai nayappittuk koḷkaiyil viruppillātāḷ pōla avvāṟu kōṭalaiyē
          virumpuvāḷ, atu taṉakku muṭiyātu eṉat talaimakaḷ puṟaṉuraittāḷ eṉak kēṭṭa parattai avaṭkup
          pāṅkāyiṉārkkuc colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink88">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>vaṇṭuṟai nayavarum vaḷamalarp poykait</l>
          <l>taṇṭuṟai yūraṉai yevvai yemvayiṉ</l>
          <l>varutal vēṇṭutu meṉpa</l>
          <l>tollēm pōlyā matuvēṇ ṭutumē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          
<l>           Our sister said that we would like him to come close to us – </l> 
<l rend="indent2">           the man from the village by the cool ghat </l> 
<l rend="indent4">             with its lush flower pond </l> 
<l rend="indent4">             where bees begin to long to linger. </l> 
<l>           [Though] we [act] as though we do not agree with what she said, </l> 
<l>           that is [exactly] what we would like. </l> 
          
          

        </lg>
      </div>
